{
  "texts": [
    "State-of-the-art analysis-AML attack typesOur study put forward an in-depth and comparative analysis based on four major adversarial attack types on machine learning.",
    "For the detailed forensics of various adversarial attack vectors, comprehensive criteria are devised to analyze each of the attack vectors and their entities in detail.",
    "Examination of each attack vector based on attack type analyzed victim threatened features, adversary, its capability and knowledge and attack vector and the severe impact of the attack vector on the victim model or algorithm.",
    "A hierarchical summary of articles studied for attack analysis is given in Fig. 10.",
    "Detailed analysis of examined attacks is given from Sections 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, and 5.4, analyzing attack vectors concerning their integrated attack type and surface."
  ]
}